{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>are you kidding me</strong></i> is a slice of life adventure with a collection of narrative driven micro games all about the inhabitants of Nowhere Space - where all lost and forgotten things end up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/theAmusementPark_establish2.gif?t=1733673154\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/castofcharacters.gif?t=1733673154\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet GoodLuck [she/her] , MothBot [he/him] Jester [he/they], Rhea [they/she], and a few more eclectic and unusual creatures\u00a0who look after the island, which takes the shape as a little amusement park!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/theAmusementPark_characters.gif?t=1733673154\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/chattotheweirdos.gif?t=1733673154\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Have very normal conversations with each to get to know them and their little worlds better. Learn to settle into and become part of this community through a short linear narrative.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/introJester.gif?t=1733673154\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/play_microgames.gif?t=1733673154\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Learn more about the world and help out it's quirky inhabitants through unusual mixed media microgames! Carry out different tasks and jobs through playing through these fast-paced funny microgames, each set, thematically cohesive &amp; comfortably fitting into the narrative.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/Jester_teeth.gif?t=1733673154\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/goodLuck_jamout.gif?t=1733673154\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Short Playtime (1-2 hours long!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An Arcade mode to let you test your skills on just the microgames</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">6 funky and fun characters with unique personalities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 50 + unique microgames!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mixed media art, using 2D and 3D assets &amp; CCO museum art</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">silly stylised art</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CONTROLS:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/y06lAP.png?t=1733673154\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/aGLU8q.png?t=1733673154\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/TucS_a.png?t=1733673154\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u00a0WASD/Arrowkeys OR L stick OR Dpad to move\u00a0</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/TucS_a.png?t=1733673154\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/aGLU8q.png?t=1733673154\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/y06lAP.png?t=1733673154\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>WASD/Arrow keys OR L stick OR Dpad to\u00a0play microgames</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/XvwnEs.png?t=1733673154\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/LxIo3I.png?t=1733673154\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>E OR X to interact/progress dialogue</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u00a0</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/nkB5TX.png?t=1733673154\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/JTdwg_.png?t=1733673154\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>ESC OR Menu to Pause the game</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/nX4Lj4.png?t=1733673154\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/extras/tm1weL.png?t=1733673154\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Y to Check objectives</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733673154","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733673154","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/b010dead24c6952bc01a1804dfab607d1aa40065/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733673154","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940440/b010dead24c6952bc01a1804dfab607d1aa40065/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733673154","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"conte